{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- I was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know exactly to-- scrounging for food and-- and a place to sleep in, I don't know-- in a hallway, a corridor.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hiding out because if they-- if they-- if they caught you, they assembled you to send you out and everything like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For about-- this went on for-- in-- you know, just-- it's almost when I watched the movie reminded me being there because being in the-- in the toilets and all these things, and that was me, you know.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my memory was when I-- when it-- when it showed in the movie when it says March 14, when the-- when the SS came over and things like that and took over the ghetto and everything.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it-- it was just like, wow, that's the day I was sent to Auschwitz-- March 14, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was almost-- it wasn't the final round-- roundup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm sure there was some people left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But almost rounded up everybody and that's when I was sent to Auschwitz in-- in open trucks, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On-- on-- in a hallway, in the streets, maybe in some houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because a lot of-- there was houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People wasn't living there anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were houses that people were-- they're empty, you know, because people that lived in those houses were already sent, were in camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were-- there were empty houses and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's where you-- wherever you found an open door you lay down and went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I'll be honest with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know I must have eaten-- I must've eaten, otherwise I wouldn't be around here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't remember where or what or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like wires.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
